-link" data-ga4="Read Next button clicks" data-testid="image-link" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"><div class="css-79elbk"><span class="css-rwmw5v css-1pf0x3y"><span class="css-1767n2d"><lazy-image alt="What to know about jet lag and headaches" src="https://media.post.rvohealth.io/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2024/07/jet-lag-GettyImages-2165552504-Thumb.jpg" srcset="https://media.post.rvohealth.io/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2024/07/jet-lag-GettyImages-2165552504-Thumb.jpg 200w" classname="css-1lyqwde"></lazy-image></span></span><span class="css-1fb1nmp"><span class="css-a10gts"></span></span></div></a></figure><div class="css-vk2z9y"><a class="css-158nx8z" rel="nofollow" data-event="engagement|bottom page content promo click|/articles/jet-lag-headache;engagement|bottom page content promo click index|5" data-element-event="INTERNAL LINK|FOOTER|Any Page|Read This Next|LINK|What to know about jet lag and headaches|rn4" href="https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/jet-lag-headache?utm_source=ReadNext" data-testid="title-link" data-ga4="Read Next button clicks">What to know about jet lag and headaches</a><section data-testid="byline" class="css-ni3p9e"><div class="css-2ch55m"><div class="css-qrw4c2"><lazy-image alt="" src="https://media.post.rvohealth.io/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/03/Meredith-Goodwin-500x500-Bio.png"></lazy-image></div></div><div><span><span>Medically reviewed by <a class="css-u1nnpx" href="https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/reviewers">Meredith Goodwin, MD, FAAFP</a></span></span></div></section><p><a class="css-kyfxln" rel="nofollow" data-event="engagement|bottom page content promo click|/articles/jet-lag-headache;engagement|bottom page content promo click index|5" data-element-event="INTERNAL LINK|FOOTER|Any Page|Read This Next|LINK|What to know about jet lag and headaches|rn4" href="https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/jet-lag-headache?utm_source=ReadNext" data-testid="text-link" data-ga4="Read Next button clicks" aria-hidden="true" tabindex